data.description: Home, Home on the Range....this is the quintessential Sierra foothill property that you've been longing to call home! Set on 40 usable acres the home is on a gentle knoll at the end of a long, private driveway. Your horses & livestock happily grazing amongst the beautiful oaks. Plenty of room for an additional guest cottage up to 1,600 sf to be built on this property for family, friends or full time ranch hand. Walk to Finnon Lake Restaurant & campgrounds and fly in to the Swansboro (01CL) AirStrip. Discover the old rock bridge, the natural spring, the seasonal creek for gold panning, Summerfield Ditch & enjoy the microclimates that this acreage offers. Room for solar panels, a poultry palace, orchard, vegetable garden, & even a pool to create that self sustainable lifestyle you've been yearning for! The detached 1,200 sf garage/shop with bathroom is nestled under the oaks for shade so you'll be comfortable year round tinkering on your projects. Don't miss this unique homestead property. Build a California Ranch legacy for your family. Check out the new 90M canyon top to canyon top bridge that this rural mountain community is receiving from Department of Transportation. Buyer to verify all information. Insurance quoted at $4801/year with Cal
